  "description": "B003 Blessed — the Leash Mechanism as performance instrument. At rest: leash 0.55, the uncanny middle from OURO-II — not noise, not pitch, suspended between states. Mod wheel sweeps leash from 0.3 (raw chaos, all attractor) to 0.8 (near-periodic, almost a tone). Aftertouch opens injection 0→0.18: the attractor receives a heartbeat, exactly OURO-I's unopened door swinging wide. The performer navigates the full spectrum of order in a single gesture: chaos at heel, tone at crown.",
